r using Steam's \"Remote Play Together\" feature.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738540/extras/2995832c134b0b79129395e6cf6399d2.poster.avif?t=1749674347\" width=616 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738540/extras/2995832c134b0b79129395e6cf6399d2.webm?t=1749674347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738540/extras/2995832c134b0b79129395e6cf6399d2.mp4?t=1749674347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game modes</h2>There are 2 modes to play alone and 1 game mode to play in multiplayer.<br><br><br>\"Playlist\": In this single-player game mode, you have an infinite number of life points, but you lose points each time you get hit, which will affect your final score. The objective is to succeed in completing all the levels by obtaining the best possible score.<br><br>\"Infinity\": In this single-player game mode, you only have one life point and your goal is to survive as long as possible. Be careful, because the speed of the music increases every 15 seconds, which has the effect of increasing the difficulty at the same time. Your best time is saved at the end of each game in an online scoreboard. You can then compare your ranking with your friends and other players.<br><br>\"Multiplayer\": In this multiplayer game mode, you can play with 2 to 4 players. All players have infinite life points, but lose points each time they get hit, which will affect their final score. Powers, like shockwaves, will appear all over the cube to make the game a little more interesting. It is possible to steal a player's power by jumping on their head.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738540/extras/39cf539992117933025bcf923ec1fb8b.poster.avif?t=1749674347\" width=616 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738540/extras/39cf539992117933025bcf923ec1fb8b.webm?t=1749674347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738540/extras/39cf539992117933025bcf923ec1fb8b.mp4?t=1749674347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Creative mode<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create custom levels using the Creative mode and let your friends test them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738540/extras/f4dcb4dce6897063b7822bcc43e5dfc3.poster.avif?t=1749674347\" width=616 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738540/extras/f4dcb4dce6897063b7822bcc43e5dfc3.webm?t=1749674347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738540/extras/f4dcb4dce6897063b7822bcc43e5dfc3.mp4?t=1749674347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Video musics</h2>- Beyond your dreams by B.Zuccone & J.Dubrez<br>- Sonic boom by Nicolas Bianco<br>- Make it happen by Cochu<br>- Sprung by Cochu<br>- Need a Break by Cochu<br>- Don't Go by Cochu<br>- Power by MANØ<br>- Last Hope by Xyrone ft. John C.<br>- Lost Woods by Xyrone ft. John C.<br>- Millennials by Xyrone ft. John C.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738540/extras/3eb305795eea1e82e24b3d57f74cb85c.poster.avif?t=1749674347\" width=616 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1738540/extras/3eb305795eea1e82e24b3d57f74cb85c.webm?t=1749674347\" type=\"video/webm; c